Hill, Vernon W. - The Wall Street Transcript













































 





































Vernon W. Hill
VERNON W. HILL II is Chairman and President and Founder of
Commerce Bancorp, Inc., which was launched in 1973 with the
opening of its first branch in Marlton, New Jersey. He was named
‘Community Banker of the Year’ by American Banker for 2000. Mr.
Hill is a graduate of the Wharton School, University of
Pennsylvania.
