                                                    BRIEF-Republic First Bancorp reports Q2 earnings per share $0.04
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    6:06 PM ET 07/20/2017
                                                


Republic First Bancorp Inc (FRBK). * Republic First Bancorp, Inc. Reports second quarter financial results. * Q2 earnings per share $0.04. * Q2 revenue rose 37 percent to $22.3 million. * Republic First Bancorp Inc (FRBK) - Qtrly net interest income $15.3 versus $11.6 million Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    Republic First Bancorp, Inc. Reports Second Quarter Financial Results
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    5:28 PM ET 07/20/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, July 20, 2017  Republic First Bancorp (FRBK), Inc., the holding company for Republic Bank, today announced its financial results for the period ended June 30, 2017. Vernon W. Hill, II, Chairman of Republic First Bancorp (FRBK) said: "The Power of Red is Back expansion campaign continues to deliver strong results.

















                                                    Republic Bank Opens New Store in Sicklerville, NJ
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    11:22 AM ET 07/18/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, July 18, 2017  Republic First Bancorp, Inc. (FRBK), the parent company of Republic Bank, opened a store in Sicklerville, NJ at 610 Berlin Cross Keys Road on Saturday, July 15. Marking the second of five new stores set to open this year throughout the Greater Philadelphia region, the Sicklerville location touts Republic Bank's signature all-glass cube design.

















                                                    Republic First Bancorp, Inc. Adds Andrew B. Cohen to Board of Directors
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    3:16 PM ET 06/29/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, June 29, 2017  Republic First Bancorp, Inc. (FRBK), the parent company of Republic Bank, today announced that Andrew B. Cohen has joined the company's Board of Directors.

















                                                    Republic Bank Opens Second Store in Cherry Hill, NJ
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:11 PM ET 06/26/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, June 26, 2017 /PRNewswire/ -- Republic First Bancorp, Inc. (FRBK), the parent company of Republic Bank, opened its second store location in Cherry Hill at 457 Haddonfield Road on Saturday, June 24. Featuring Republic Bank's renowned all-glass cube design, this marks the first of five new stores set to open in 2017 throughout the Greater Philadelphia region.

















                                                    Republic Bank Hires Sicklerville Store Manager
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    9:29 AM ET 06/15/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, June 15, 2017  Republic First Bancorp, Inc. (FRBK), the parent company of Republic Bank, today announced that Nick Knestaut was named Vice President/Store Manager for its Sicklerville, NJ location. Sicklerville team," said Harry Madonna, Chairman and CEO of Republic Bank.

















                                                    Republic Bank Hires New Store Manager for Second Cherry Hill Location
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    2:33 PM ET 05/10/2017
                                                


PHILADELPHIA, May 10, 2017  Republic First Bancorp, Inc. (FRBK), the parent company of Republic Bank, today announced that Gladys Santana was named Assistant Vice President/Store Manager for its second Cherry Hill location. New Jersey," said Harry Madonna, Chairman and CEO of Republic Bank.












